/* Customize tab (renamed) */
"Agents" = "代理";

/* Onboarding */
"Welcome to Vibe Coding Guard" = "欢迎使用 Vibe Coding Guard";
"It keeps your Mac awake while Codex or Claude Code is working, so long jobs finish even when you step away. Pick a mode below — you can change it anytime from the menu bar." = "当 Codex 或 Claude Code 正在工作时，它会让你的 Mac 保持唤醒，这样即使你离开，长时间的任务也能完成。请在下方选择一个模式——随时可以从菜单栏更改。";
"Get Started" = "开始使用";

/* Mode descriptions */
"Off — your Mac sleeps normally. Vibe Coding Guard does nothing until you switch it on." = "关闭——你的 Mac 正常休眠。在你重新开启之前，Vibe Coding Guard 不会做任何事。";
"Auto — stays awake only while Codex or Claude Code is running, then lets your Mac sleep." = "自动——仅在 Codex 或 Claude Code 运行时保持唤醒，之后让 Mac 休眠。";
"Always — keeps your Mac awake until you turn this off." = "始终——让你的 Mac 保持唤醒，直到你将其关闭。";

/* Inline feedback */
"Lid-closed mode needs admin approval — not enabled." = "合盖模式需要管理员授权——尚未启用。";
"Turns the screen off right away. Your work keeps running." = "立即关闭屏幕。你的任务会继续运行。";
"The warning level always stays above the critical level." = "警告值始终高于严重值。";
"Ready, but the keyboard only locks while Keep Awake is on. Set the mode to Auto or Always to use it." = "已就绪，但键盘仅在防休眠开启时才会锁定。请将模式设为“自动”或“始终”以使用此功能。";

/* Menu / About */
"Settings…" = "设置…";
"About Vibe Coding Guard" = "关于 Vibe Coding Guard";
"OK" = "好";
"Version %@\n\nKeeps your Mac awake while Codex or Claude Code is working.\n\nLid-closed mode adds one narrow sudoers rule for the exact pmset commands it needs. Remove it anytime from the Agents tab." = "版本 %@\n\n当 Codex 或 Claude Code 正在工作时，让你的 Mac 保持唤醒。\n\n合盖模式只会为其所需的特定 pmset 命令添加一条范围很窄的 sudoers 规则。你可以随时在“代理”选项卡中移除它。";

